channel.title: 317 Npc Head to Interface Packet [317 Protocol]
channel.description:
Hey everyone,
So I am trying to figure out the packet to be able to send an npc head to chat interfaces. The only packet related to that is the player head to interface (which I've already added). Can someone give me all the stuff for that packet or update the rswiki:317protocol, if you know it?
Thanks in advance.

item.title: 317 Npc Head to Interface Packet [317 Protocol]
item.dc:creator: @pure2ownage Pure_
item.description:
@pure2ownage wrote:

[quote=“Death Style, post:4, topic:544264”]Someone was providing some new info on the wiki and he mocked him saying this is already known by everyone, but clearly it isn’t. This is just another example.

I think it’s frame 75, param 1 being ID and param 2 being interface ID (4883?). I’m in the same boat and the only way I’m checking is by reviewing other sources.[/quote]Ignore him, his ego is pretty bloated.
